invalid type: string "Top Class Education For Students With Disabilities (TCE-SWD) — faq\n\n**Q: Am I eligible for this scholarship if two of my siblings are availing the benefits of this scheme?**\n\nA: No. You won't be eligible in this case.\n\n**Q: How will my tuition fee and non-refundable charges be paid?**\n\nA: The payment will be made directly to the institution.\n\nf my application?**\n